06:47.992 --> 06:49.983
Hi.
Hey.

06:50.077 --> 06:52.989
I'm sorry,
family members only
during procedures.

06:53.539 --> 06:54.995
I'll wait outside.

06:55.082 --> 06:57.619
Oh, no, please,
it's okay.

06:57.710 --> 07:01.248
Joseph helps me
with my husband sometimes.

07:02.464 --> 07:03.544
He's a good friend.

07:03.632 --> 07:06.214
Which means not family.

07:06.844 --> 07:08.254
Wait, we're gonna
be here a while.

07:08.345 --> 07:11.508
Why don't you
show Joseph where
the visitor's lounge is?

07:11.599 --> 07:12.839
Okay.

07:18.522 --> 07:19.602
What?

07:20.274 --> 07:22.515
I'm surprised
you didn't go into
the diplomatic corps.

07:22.610 --> 07:24.817
Oh, you think they're...

07:26.905 --> 07:27.940
No.
If they're having sex,

07:28.032 --> 07:29.693
it's probably
with their genitals.

07:31.493 --> 07:35.532
