You know that close to
1% of the population
identifies as asexual?

07:44.423 --> 07:47.290
We really got to
get you laid.

07:47.384 --> 07:50.046
If I have to plow
that furrow myself,
so be it.

07:50.137 --> 07:52.378
I've a patient
who's asexual.

07:52.473 --> 07:54.680
Is she a giant pool
of algae?

07:54.767 --> 07:56.974
It's a valid
sexual orientation,

07:57.061 --> 07:58.551
according to this article,
at least.

07:58.854 --> 08:01.971
Yeah,
I think I read that, too.
Is that Fug/iness Week/y?

08:02.066 --> 08:03.806
She's perfectly
fine-looking.

08:03.901 --> 08:04.981
Happily married
for 10 years.

08:05.069 --> 08:07.151
To a guy who
loves penis enough
for both of them.

08:08.280 --> 08:09.440
He's asexual, too.

08:10.574 --> 08:11.939
Ran a complete
physical on her.

08:12.034 --> 08:14.275
Nothing wrong
except a common
bladder infection.

08:16.997 --> 08:20.034
Hundred bucks says
I can find a medical reason

08:20.125 --> 08:21.205
why she doesn't want
to have sex.

08:21.293 --> 08:22.794
You're out of your mind
if you think

08:22.878 --> 08:24.584
l'm letting you anywhere
near my patient.

08:24.672 --> 08:26.082
Fine, I won't go near her.

08:26.173 --> 08:29.961
Just give me her file
and any blood samples
you have left over.

08:32.846 --> 08:36.680
No contact whatsoever.
You talk to her,
the bet is void.

08:36.767 --> 08:40.305
No contact. Plays to
my strengths, anyway.

08:45.192 --> 08:46.398
(DOOR SLlDES OPEN)

08:47.611 --> 08:49.112
Right now's not
a good time, House.

08:49.196 --> 08:50.902
Not for the Dean
of Medicine,

08:50.989 --> 08:53.366
but it's the perfect time
if you're a member
of my team.

08:53.450 --> 08:55.236
Which one are you?

08:56.495 --> 08:58.326
What did
the endoscopy show?

08:59.123 --> 09:01.034
No signs of
ulcers or blockages.

09:01.125 --> 09:02.456
(BEEPING)

09:05.587 --> 09:08.203
But you found a tear
just below the esophagus.

09:08.298 --> 09:09.378
Explains the bleeding.

09:09.466 --> 09:12.253
Doesn't explain why
he vomited so hard
he ripped his insides.

09:12.344 --> 09:15.051
His liver enzymes
are slightly elevated.
Gallstones could...

09:15.139 --> 09:16.470
No complaints of pain.

09:16.557 --> 09:20.049
Steatohepatitis
would make his AST
and ATL levels rise.

09:21.228 --> 09:22.889
Are you calling
his liver fat?

09:24.273 --> 09:25.558
Start the patient
on statins,

09:25.649 --> 09:26.980
do a biopsy
to confirm.

09:27.067 --> 09:28.932
And knock him out,
I've heard
he's a wiggler.

09:29.027 --> 09:30.107
There's no need
to put him under.

09:30.195 --> 09:33.358
We can confirm fatty liver
with an ultrasound.

09:36.952 --> 09:39.989
Well done. And now,
as a member of my team,

09:40.080 --> 09:43.117
you can make the equally
useful observations
that the sky is blue,

09:43.208 --> 09:46.666
I'm wearing pants,
and I'm ignoring
your first observation.

09:47.045 --> 09:48.125
Of course.

09:53.927 --> 09:54.916
Wait.

09:55.012 --> 09:56.468
And there it is.

09:56.847 --> 09:58.587
You're trying to screw
with my confidence.

09:58.682 --> 09:59.717
Well, if I wanted
to do that,

09:59.808 --> 10:01.423
I'd tell you how much
the nurses hate you.

10:01.518 --> 10:04.134
You're trying to get me
to define myself
as a subordinate

10:04.229 --> 10:06.094
to keep me from
ever intervening,

10:06.190 --> 10:08.476
even if it's fully
in the scope
of my duties.

10:08.567 --> 10:10.853
Like now. This isn't
about diagnostics,

10:10.944 --> 10:12.195
it's about what's safe
for the patient.

10:12.696 --> 10:13.902
Do the ultrasound.

10:15.032 --> 10:16.818
Ultrasound it is.

10:17.618 --> 10:18.983
And the nurses
love you.

10:23.791 --> 10:26.077
You don't think I knew
House was gonna tell you
to ignore me

10:26.168 --> 10:27.658
and not do
the ultrasound?

10:28.128 --> 10:29.504
This is an
ultrasound machine.

10:29.588 --> 10:32.295
Which you're gonna use to do
an ultrasound-guided biopsy.

10:32.883 --> 10:35.750
You've probably got
a kit stashed here...

10:44.394 --> 10:49.013
"Cuddy Dark will
waste his afternoon
chasing conspiracy theories."

10:49.107 --> 10:51.018
You're letting him
get inside your head.

10:51.109 --> 10:52.974
He can do a lot
of damage in there.

10:54.488 --> 10:58.026
Dr. Chase,
he started vomiting again.

11:00.702 --> 11:02.988
This is why we stopped
the antiemetics.

11:03.080 --> 11:04.661
We needed to see if
it was still a symptom.

11:04.748 --> 11:05.908
Okay.

11:06.875 --> 11:08.411
Here. You want this?

11:08.502 --> 11:11.619
Get your hands off me.
You're taking my head!

11:12.714 --> 11:15.922
It's okay, Andres.
You're in the hospital.

11:18.804 --> 11:19.919
(GRUNTING)

11:21.431 --> 11:22.466
(GLASS SHATTERING)

11:22.558 --> 11:23.968
10 milligrams
of diazepam.

11:24.059 --> 11:25.424
