11:25.519 --> 11:27.225
Hey!
NATALIE:
I'm fine. I'm fine.

11:31.191 --> 11:32.476
(PANTlNG)

11:33.318 --> 11:34.854
Foreman.

11:34.945 --> 11:36.606
FOREMAN:
Blood in his urine.

11:42.494 --> 11:45.327
JESSICA:
We resumed the antiemetics
and increased his sedation.

11:45.414 --> 11:46.620
He really
went after her.

11:46.707 --> 11:48.698
Maybe he found out
about her "good friend."

11:48.792 --> 11:51.374
It was just paranoid rage.
Typical of Alzheimer's.

11:51.461 --> 11:52.917
We don't even know
if they were
sleeping together.

11:53.005 --> 11:55.087
A few hours ago,
you were sure.

11:55.173 --> 11:57.380
And that's
significant why?

11:57.467 --> 12:00.083
Sorry, only the bleeding's
medically relevant.

12:00.178 --> 12:01.554
No, I wasn't
being rhetorical.

12:01.638 --> 12:05.631
If they are
sleeping together,
why do we disapprove?

12:06.685 --> 12:08.425
You're pro infidelity?

12:08.520 --> 12:09.680
She's not married.

12:11.481 --> 12:13.733
