and cleaning someone

12:13.817 --> 12:17.309
and limiting conversation
to repeating a few
simple commands,

12:17.404 --> 12:19.110
then I was married
to my pet rat.

12:19.197 --> 12:21.688
And a lot of people
owe me wedding gifts.

12:21.825 --> 12:23.690
And we're walking,
we're walking.

12:23.827 --> 12:27.240
I don't care how sick
your spouse gets,
you don'tjump ship.

12:27.331 --> 12:30.323
Alzheimer's is different.
She can't share
her problems with him,

12:30.417 --> 12:32.783
or plan for the future.
The man she married
no longer exists.

12:32.878 --> 12:34.334
Yes, he does.
He's in there.

12:34.421 --> 12:36.503
This is why
you get married.

12:36.673 --> 12:39.255
Said the divorced woman
to the divorced man.

12:39.343 --> 12:43.586
I didn'tjump ship.
My husband sank it
when he cheated on me.

12:43.680 --> 12:45.261
Commitment's
not conditional.

12:45.349 --> 12:48.182
She is there for him
in the only way
that matters now.

12:48.310 --> 12:49.595
She gave up her life
to take care of him.

12:49.686 --> 12:50.801
Proves she's an idiot.

12:50.896 --> 12:53.103
If she had any sense,
she'd have stuck him
in a facility

12:53.190 --> 12:54.600
and jumped
on that strange...

12:54.691 --> 12:57.307
Dr. Foreman.
We were just
looking for you.

12:57.402 --> 12:59.313
