your index cards
actually predicted

13:31.687 --> 13:32.893
the guy was
gonna punch his wife,

13:33.021 --> 13:36.058
everything you're saying is
post hoc rationalization.

13:36.191 --> 13:39.729
Dr. Park,
would you please reach
under that chair?

13:43.240 --> 13:45.071
"The patient will
punch his wife."

13:46.910 --> 13:48.741
