relationships with men.

16:57.100 --> 16:59.056
(LAUGHS)
Not a lot of them.

16:59.144 --> 17:01.760
We've run every test
and ruled out
all the options.

17:01.855 --> 17:04.312
You're gonna have to accept
she just doesn't want sex.

17:04.399 --> 17:05.764
Lots of people
don't have sex.

17:05.859 --> 17:07.190
The only people
who don't want it

17:07.277 --> 17:08.858
