dead or lying.

17:08.945 --> 17:10.276
So maybe she's lying.

17:10.363 --> 17:12.149
You think she's had
a boyfriend on the side?

17:12.240 --> 17:13.320
For 10 years?

17:13.408 --> 17:16.616
