22:52.622 --> 22:56.490
So do I wish
Mom had used a gun
instead of a bottle?

22:56.626 --> 22:57.832
Yes.

23:01.130 --> 23:02.336
I didn't know.

23:02.423 --> 23:03.799
That's why I told you.

23:05.301 --> 23:06.290
(MONITOR BEEPING)

23:06.386 --> 23:08.468
Ventricular fibrillation.

23:11.975 --> 23:14.182
Give him 300 milligrams
amiodarone.

23:21.985 --> 23:23.065
(DEFIBRILLATOR CHARGING)

23:24.862 --> 23:26.989
Be careful.
Once we establish rhythm,

23:27.073 --> 23:29.485
any accidental movement
could crash him back
into V-fib.

23:36.958 --> 23:37.947
