23:42.547 --> 23:44.959
We still have
a long way to go.

23:45.049 --> 23:46.630
Cold can be protective
to the brain,

23:46.718 --> 23:50.085
but there is
a possibility
of damage.

23:50.179 --> 23:54.513
We also need to confirm
and treat whatever's
making him sick.

23:56.853 --> 23:59.185
I just gotta do
a standard battery of tests.

23:59.272 --> 24:01.354
Blood, urine, EEG.

24:01.441 --> 24:03.773
