telling a guy he has a tumor
growing in his head?

29:55.711 --> 29:58.088
He'll notice it eventually
when it starts leaking
out his ears.

29:58.172 --> 29:59.537
It's a slow-growing tumor.

29:59.632 --> 30:01.623
