his ankle monitor off?

30:24.699 --> 30:26.109
On your desk.

30:29.370 --> 30:30.655
(SIGHS)

30:44.427 --> 30:45.792
You played me.

30:45.886 --> 30:48.298
This whole thing was
about your ankle monitor.

30:49.306 --> 30:50.967
You weren't trying to
undermine my confidence,

30:51.058 --> 30:52.138
you were trying
to inflate it.

30:52.226 --> 30:54.512
