conflict with me

30:54.603 --> 30:55.934
so, eventually,
you could let me win.

30:56.397 --> 30:57.728
You knew
it was encephalitis,

30:57.815 --> 30:58.850
but you waited
for me to say it,

30:58.941 --> 31:00.272
because then,
with my ego boosted,

31:00.359 --> 31:02.270
you thought
I'd be in the mood
to take off your monitor.

31:02.361 --> 31:04.272
