Take off my monitor.

31:12.455 --> 31:14.411
See, the beauty
of the plan

31:14.498 --> 31:17.205
is if it works,
then you think
you can control me.

31:17.293 --> 31:20.035
If it fails,
then you will actually

31:20.129 --> 31:22.211
