you can control me.

31:22.965 --> 31:24.080
It's pretty genius.

31:25.384 --> 31:28.421
These are
your training wheels.

31:28.512 --> 31:31.003
If you think
you're up to this job,
it's time to lose them.

31:45.029 --> 31:46.940
Second half of my plan
might need work.

31:48.157 --> 31:49.818
(PAGERS BEEPING)

31:53.579 --> 31:55.319
