is worth a lot
to this hospital,

32:29.073 --> 32:31.689
'cause we're
wasting a crapload
of time and man power

32:31.784 --> 32:33.615
just to let this guy
watch his mind shrivel

32:33.702 --> 32:34.828
and keep
his wife miserable.

32:34.912 --> 32:37.779
Heart attack while
he was on interferon
rules out encephalitis,

32:37.873 --> 32:40.125
but I still think
I'm right about
the neuro symptoms.

32:40.209 --> 32:41.824
It's probably
aseptic meningitis.

32:41.919 --> 32:43.284
We would have
seen meningeal signs.

32:43.379 --> 32:45.290
Given his
abnormal mental status,
not necessarily.

32:45.422 --> 32:48.255
Dr. Foreman!
Would you please
reach under your chair?

32:54.181 --> 32:55.967
It's just wet gum
under here.

32:56.100 --> 32:57.931
Where's the card?
What card?

33:00.479 --> 33:04.063
I'm happy to leave
if you have a better theory
than aseptic meningitis.

33:04.150 --> 33:05.265
Toxins.

33:05.359 --> 33:06.690
If this guy went
on a walkabout,

33:06.777 --> 33:08.062
chances are
he's done it before.

33:08.154 --> 33:09.189
Wife keeps the doors
in the house locked.

33:09.280 --> 33:10.645
There's plenty of
nasty stuff to get into

33:10.739 --> 33:11.899
during the middle
of the night.

33:11.991 --> 33:13.151
We asked about toxins
on the history.

33:13.242 --> 33:15.733
The wife said she was sure
to clear the house
for her husband's safety.

33:15.828 --> 33:16.943
And I'm sure
she succeeded.

33:17.037 --> 33:19.028
She's a PhD
in toxicology, right?

33:20.332 --> 33:23.165
She's an ex-florist.
Search the home
for toxic plants,

33:23.252 --> 33:25.038
methyl bromide,
any medications.

33:26.297 --> 33:29.334
Stop.
You're not infallible.

33:29.425 --> 33:30.460
You were wrong
about encephalitis.

33:30.551 --> 33:31.540
Just before you were.

33:31.635 --> 33:34.172
Run CSF tests,
find out what's causing
the meningitis.

33:36.390 --> 33:38.676
You said you weren't
gonna overrule me,
diagnostically.

33:38.767 --> 33:41.179
And you said
I wouldn't be able
to help it.

33:41.270 --> 33:43.181
Apparently, you were
right about that one.

33:45.774 --> 33:48.607
Fine. I'll look
for toxins myself.

33:48.694 --> 33:50.730
You can't go
to their house without
Foreman's permission.

33:50.821 --> 33:54.609
Don't need it,
I'm gonna talk to
the toxicology PhD upstairs.

33:54.700 --> 33:56.736
HOUSE: What about gifts
from South America?

33:56.827 --> 33:59.318
Anyone send any
fruits or vegetables?

34:00.164 --> 34:01.574
I don't think so... No.

34:01.916 --> 34:03.622
(ANDRES MUTTERING
IN PORTUGUESE)

34:05.294 --> 34:08.707
I'm gonna need
your boyfriend to
collect samples of plants

34:08.797 --> 34:11.174
in and around your house.
Toxins are the most...

34:14.720 --> 34:16.551
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

34:17.556 --> 34:21.219
Wait. You understand him?
What's he saying?

34:23.354 --> 34:26.312
He's repeating
"blue shack."

34:26.815 --> 34:28.066
You know what that is?

34:28.150 --> 34:30.436
Is it somewhere
where pesticides
may be kept?

34:32.279 --> 34:35.146
It's where
we had our first date.

34:35.449 --> 34:37.064
(CONHNUESSPEAMNG
PORTUGUESE)

34:37.993 --> 34:41.986
Do you have a cleaning lady
who might bring
her own supplies?

34:42.831 --> 34:44.082
What's he saying?

34:44.750 --> 34:48.242
If it's not relevant to
the case, I don't care,
and neither should you.

34:48.337 --> 34:49.747
Please.

34:50.589 --> 34:52.875
This might be
the last time I ever know
what he's thinking.

35:01.558 --> 35:03.094
(TRANSLATING)
"When I saw her waiting...

35:05.187 --> 35:07.143
"Waiting for me
at the table...

35:08.774 --> 35:11.607
"The way her eyes looked
when she smiled...

35:14.738 --> 35:16.239
"I felt like crying.

35:21.370 --> 35:24.407
"I knew
she was the woman
I wanted to marry.

35:25.457 --> 35:28.824
"And every time
I see her, I say...

35:32.256 --> 35:34.793
"There she is."
"There she is."

35:40.014 --> 35:42.175
He's still in there.

35:42.975 --> 35:44.215
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

35:46.979 --> 35:48.719
What did he say?

35:50.691 --> 35:52.682
He asked who you were.

35:56.405 --> 35:58.441
Don't get your hopes up.

35:59.074 --> 36:02.032
Have your boyfriend
get me those samples.

36:12.463 --> 36:14.169
How did you even know
to look for a tumor?

36:15.716 --> 36:18.628
Dr. House noticed
hormone levels
in your blood

36:18.719 --> 36:20.630
and consulted with me
as an oncologist...

36:20.721 --> 36:22.427
Who cares how
they found it, okay?
They found it.

36:23.807 --> 36:25.343
Are there any side effects
to the treatment?

36:26.643 --> 36:30.636
Some nausea, dizziness,
and as the tumor shrinks,

36:30.731 --> 36:32.687
there will be
behavioral changes.

36:32.983 --> 36:34.519
Like what?

36:34.610 --> 36:35.941
Well...

36:36.904 --> 36:40.271
The tumor interferes with
certain natural systems.

36:43.827 --> 36:46.944
It lowers libido
and causes
erectile dysfunction.

36:50.250 --> 36:54.584
You mean the treatment
will make me want
to have sex?

36:57.383 --> 36:58.748
What if I don't
want the treatment?

36:58.842 --> 37:00.457
I would
strongly advise...

37:00.552 --> 37:02.258
Look, you have
a brain tumor, okay?

37:02.346 --> 37:03.381
You have to
have the treatment.

37:03.472 --> 37:05.838
Okay, look,
I know who I am, okay?

37:05.933 --> 37:07.013
And I'm not one of them.

37:07.101 --> 37:09.843
Hey, look,
we'll adjust.

37:09.937 --> 37:13.145
Okay? We can go
through this together.

37:13.232 --> 37:16.599
You mean have sex?
I can't make you do that.

37:17.569 --> 37:19.400
Maybe it won't
be so bad.

37:19.488 --> 37:20.898
It'll be terrible.

37:22.741 --> 37:25.403
It's actually
pretty fun.

37:28.247 --> 37:30.158
From what I remember.

37:30.999 --> 37:32.660
But you said that...
I know.

37:33.627 --> 37:36.915
I know. Iwanted to
spend my life with you

37:38.006 --> 37:40.668
and I knew that meant
making certain sacrifices.

37:41.844 --> 37:45.052
But a girl has needs.

37:50.227 --> 37:52.343
You dropped
in the US. News rankings.

37:52.438 --> 37:55.601
With respect,
Mr. Laffont, that's only
because we temporarily

37:55.732 --> 37:57.268
shut down our
diagnostics department.

37:57.359 --> 37:58.644
It's up
and running again.

37:58.735 --> 38:01.317
I'm actually concerned
it might be because of
the change in management.

38:01.405 --> 38:04.943
If you want my money,
I'll need to see
a five year plan.

38:09.246 --> 38:10.326
Am I boring you?

38:12.541 --> 38:17.911
No, Ijust,
those flowers are
from last week.

38:18.005 --> 38:19.996
They should
be dead by now.

38:20.090 --> 38:21.170
Excuse me?

38:24.595 --> 38:25.960
Sorry, I have to go.

38:38.192 --> 38:39.648
It's Reye's Syndrome.

38:39.735 --> 38:42.397
Patient had a sore throat
a few weeks ago
before he was admitted.

38:42.488 --> 38:44.729
Reye's in adults
is a reach.

38:44.823 --> 38:45.938
Not if he took aspirin.

38:46.033 --> 38:48.194
Aspirin in adults
is a reach.

38:48.285 --> 38:50.401
Especially in a house
with locked medicine cabinets.

38:50.496 --> 38:51.827
It wasn't in
the medicine cabinet.

38:51.914 --> 38:54.326
The wife used to
run a floral company,

38:54.416 --> 38:55.826
still does a few orders
from home.

38:55.918 --> 38:57.783
She uses crushed aspirin
in the water

38:57.878 --> 38:59.709
to make the flowers
last longer.

39:02.007 --> 39:03.668
So the husband
has a sore throat,

39:03.759 --> 39:05.340
takes an aspirin
without her knowing,

39:05.427 --> 39:07.292
realizes he's
got a sore throat,
takes an aspirin,

39:07.387 --> 39:08.638
realizes he's got
a sore throat...

39:08.722 --> 39:11.179
You can stop me
whenever you like.

39:12.351 --> 39:14.342
Have Chase start him
on steroids.

39:14.436 --> 39:16.097
I already did.

39:17.105 --> 39:18.561
Then why are
you telling me?

39:18.649 --> 39:20.685
Because I wanted you
to hear it from me.

39:37.209 --> 39:38.415
(SIGHS)

39:51.473 --> 39:53.384
There she is.

39:54.810 --> 39:55.970
(SIGHS)

39:56.144 --> 39:58.100
Here I am.

40:00.774 --> 40:03.607
Your eye.
What happened?

40:06.280 --> 40:08.612
It's nothing
I can't handle.

40:21.837 --> 40:24.920
MRI confirmed
macroprolactinoma.

40:25.882 --> 40:27.088
He's doing the treatment.

40:27.175 --> 40:28.301
And the wife?

40:36.059 --> 40:40.223
Come on.
We saved a man's life,

40:40.314 --> 40:44.148
course-corrected
two people's wildly
screwed up worldviews.

40:45.319 --> 40:47.275
Notbad
for a day's work.

40:50.866 --> 40:54.825
I think they were happy,
even if it was based
on lies.

40:54.911 --> 40:56.742
Most happiness is.

40:59.916 --> 41:01.417
Better to have shtupped
andlost

41:01.501 --> 41:03.366
than never to
have shtupped at all.

41:04.421 --> 41:05.957
We can't smoke in here.

41:10.218 --> 41:12.880
We also can't summon
people into the clinic
based on a lie

41:12.971 --> 41:16.304
motivated by a petty bet,
and yet it happens.

41:16.391 --> 41:18.552
It's an imperfect world.

41:30.072 --> 41:31.312
Well?

41:31.990 --> 41:33.571
Disgustingly satisfying.

41:35.827 --> 41:36.816
(KNOCKING ON DOOR)

41:37.245 --> 41:38.234
(DOOR OPENS)

41:40.832 --> 41:41.912
He said it was okay.

41:42.000 --> 41:44.082
Is one of you Dr. House?

41:45.337 --> 41:46.747
You've seen Spartacus,
right?

41:46.838 --> 41:49.830
I got an order here to
deactivate and remove
his ankle monitor.

41:50.717 --> 41:52.423
(SLOW POP SONG PLAYING)

41:58.725 --> 41:59.760
(CELL PHONE BEEPS)

41:59.851 --> 42:01.102
(RINGING TONE)

42:03.605 --> 42:04.845
(OVER PHON E) Robbie?

42:04.940 --> 42:06.271
Hey, sis.

42:08.443 --> 42:10.058
It’s been years.

42:10.153 --> 42:11.438
I know.

42:12.114 --> 42:14.776
I thought of you
on Mom's birthday.

42:15.784 --> 42:17.775
Is everything okay?

42:17.869 --> 42:20.326
Yeah, yeah.
Fine. Ijust...

42:21.957 --> 42:24.699
...wanted to
see how you were.

42:24.793 --> 42:25.953
I’m fine.

42:40.308 --> 42:42.560
Bikes go faster
without training wheels.

42:46.857 --> 42:50.190
Now get out,
I have work to do.

42:57.993 --> 42:59.904
Whoops.
